message: Photo was captured by University of Arizona photographer at the behest of Arizona Bookstore director. As campus newspaper business manager 1965-1967, I marketed the photo. When original was lost and no copies were available (mine was lost in an arson fire in 1980), I secured an extremely faded copy. My employee at Matson Multi Media in San Antonio completely restored the color to the image as now seen. The restoration is on display on UA campus - Dean's office of the Eller College of Management.
